Commvault project manager for the Implementation of the Commvault Data management suite for Partner HDS at the European Commission in Luxembourg.

- Create project scoping and SoW; 
- Execute Discovery in customer environment to gather information for the Commvault solution;
- Creation of the Commvault Low Level Design for the Datamanagement solution;
- Setup Commvault core infrastructure for the Datamanagement solution;
- Installation of application agents for the Datamanagement solution;
- Assist customer in migrating from the legacy backup solution to the Commvault Datamanagement solution

